2. Reconnaissance & Enumeration

"We cannot exploit what we haven't identified."

The environment was established by bringing up an OpenVPN tunnel through the tun0 interface, ensuring direct connectivity with the target subnet.

2.1 Initial Port Scan with Nmap
A comprehensive scan was performed using specific flags to gather service version information and banners — essential for identifying known CVEs and the underlying OS.
